    h2 Sturm-Lioville equations
    p Find values for $E$ and $f : [a, b] \to \mathbb{R}$ such that
    | $$ - \frac{\text{d}}{\text{d} x}\left(p(x) \frac{\text{d}f}{\text{d} x}\right) + q(x) f(x) = E w(x) f(x) $$
    p with boundary conditions.
