  section
    h2 Vibrating string

    p
      | As differential equation: $\, \displaystyle \frac{\partial^2 f}{\partial t^2} = \frac{\partial^2 f}{\partial x^2}\, $ with $f(0) = 0$ and $f(1) = 0$.

    p.fragment We can write
      | $$ f(t, x) = \sum_{i=1}^\infty f_i(x) \sin\left(\sqrt{E_i} t\right) $$
      | with $\, \displaystyle -\frac{\text{d}^2 f_i}{\text{d} x^2} = E_i f_i(x)\, $ and $f_i(0) = f_i(1) = 0$.
